    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they learn how to play a Jewish music, something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was amazed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Going back the-- to my sadist, Herring, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we had to have make the norm every day so many thousands of, of ammunition we had to get out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we cannot, if for example the-- some tools were broken or something, they beat up the man who has nothing to do with it was broken.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was broken.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't have the tools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have enough, anything of anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you have to have a, a special card to go to the main office to take it, the thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I write his name, my-- To take what?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To take the, the, the tools, what broken.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the-- he says that the machine is not working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I use to bring those things back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I write his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can do everything what you want when you are in need.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
